        {
            "title": "新世界百貨執董兼CEO謝惠芳請辭 將採納領導層過渡安排",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新世界百貨中國(00825)發公告，指執行董事兼首席執行官謝惠芳已提出請辭，由2月14日起生效；公司將先採納領導曾過渡安排。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：新世界百貨官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1147x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240604_FI_source-web_00825-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新世界百貨官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1147x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240604_FI_source-web_00825-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：新世界百貨官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司表示，謝惠芳因為有意投放更多時間在個人發展上，故向公司請辭，她已確認與董事會並無意見分歧，並無與其辭任有關事項須予知會股東及聯交所。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">緊隨謝惠芳請辭及有待新任CEO獲委任前，該公司將採納領導層過渡安排，自今日起生效。在此過渡安排下，公司副主庸兼執董黃少媚將負責新世界百貨的日常管理與營運的整體領導，並向管理團隊提供策略性指導。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15582411-%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e7%99%be%e8%b2%a8%e5%9f%b7%e8%91%a3%e5%85%bcceo%e8%ac%9d%e6%83%a0%e8%8a%b3%e8%ab%8b%e8%be%ad-%e5%b0%87%e6%8e%a1%e7%b4%8d%e9%a0%98%e5%b0%8e%e5%b1%a4%e9%81%8e%e6%b8%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240604_FI_source-web_00825-704-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 17:00:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金管局：上月外匯基金境外資產減少125億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局公布，去年12月外匯基金境外資產減少125億元，降至35255億元；貨幣基礎20400億元；外匯基金對香港私營部門的債權總額3881億元，對外負債總額523億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15582441-%e9%87%91%e7%ae%a1%e5%b1%80%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%a4%96%e5%8c%af%e5%9f%ba%e9%87%91%e5%a2%83%e5%a4%96%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a2%e6%b8%9b%e5%b0%91125%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKMA-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 17:00:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中信銀行2025年業績快報：純利按年升2.98%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中信銀行(00998)發表2025年度業績快報，顯示根據中國會計準則，去年歸屬銀行股東淨利潤706.18億元(人民幣．下同)，按年微升2.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20230824_FI_source_licensed_00998_shutterstock_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20230824_FI_source_licensed_00998_shutterstock_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內營業總收入約2127.74億元，則較2024年度減少0.55%。營業利潤836.74億元，按年增長3.39%；利潤總額840.43億元，也增長3.93%。歸屬銀行股東並扣除非經常性損益的淨利潤為98.19億元，按年增長2.58%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至去年底，中信銀行不良貸款率1.15%，比2024年底下降0.01個百分點；撥備覆蓋率203.61%，按年下降5.82個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15582337-%e4%b8%ad%e4%bf%a1%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c2025%e5%b9%b4%e6%a5%ad%e7%b8%be%e5%bf%ab%e5%a0%b1%ef%bc%9a%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%872-98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20230824_FI_source_licensed_00998_shutterstock_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 16:50:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "賽晶科技發盈喜 料去年純利增長約30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">賽晶科技(00580)發盈喜，預期2025年度母公司擁有人應佔溢利，將錄得按年增長約30%；收入預期達22.5億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升約40%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：賽晶科技2024年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/00580.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：賽晶科技2024年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/00580.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：賽晶科技2024年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司表示，去年盈利提升，主要因為收入增加導致毛利提升，再加上其他收入及收益增加，當中主要包括匯兌收益及為降低以外幣進行採購的匯兌風險而簽訂的外匯遠期合約收益。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內收入增加，則主要因為來自柔性輸電業務領域的收入增加，得益於有關工程訂單產品陸續交付及收入確認；另外，自產絕緣柵雙極型晶體管的收入增加也有助業績。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15582304-%e8%b3%bd%e6%99%b6%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e7%b4%8430",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/00580-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 16:45:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收升31點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收6.9734，較上日官方收盤價漲31點，較上日夜盤收盤漲61點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15582298-%e5%9c%a8%e5%b2%b8%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3%e5%85%8c%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%8731%e9%bb%9e-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/200101_FI_RMB_3_FB-1-1-1-1-2-2-1-1-2-1-1_source-licensed__704px.jpg.webp",
